something in me,

26:09.330 --> 26:12.960
practically dragged me off
a barstool to a meeting.

26:12.960 --> 26:17.170
Whatever is was,
it stuck.

26:17.170 --> 26:19.920
You see something
in this girl,

26:19.920 --> 26:21.670
you go ahead
and drag her.

26:21.670 --> 26:24.120
Now, it might now work,

26:24.120 --> 26:27.290
