29:26.210 --> 29:27.790
It's her heart and soul
that went into it.

29:27.790 --> 29:30.580
I mean, it's not as easy as just
giving back an award, you know?

29:30.580 --> 29:32.290
You think that
was easy?

29:32.290 --> 29:33.500
